== Overview ==
This miniature nuclear reactor can generate enough power to drive the medium Bot types but is likely too heavy for the lighter types. It has a balance between reserve power and recharge.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Sub-Nuclear Reactor can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.

